column2: Water high-staff gauge not yet installed
Secchi reading about the same as '94 + '95.
Weather cool - very little boat traffic.
Weather excellent- fishing good- boat traffic moderate.
Water temp. 80 degrees @ 3'-light activity-5 loons on lake.
Lowest water level this year-water temp. 80 degrees @ 3'.
Weather nice but 8-10 degrees below normal. water temp. 80 degrees @ 3'-little boating activity.
Weather excellent-2.5"+ rain earlier in week. moderate boating activity.
78 degrees- wind NW @ 18-20 mph. 8 persons at beach.
75 degrees- wind NW @ 12 mph-very little activity on lake-clearest water in 3 weeks. partly cloudy.
85 degrees- wind S @ 5 mph- sunny beautiful day- water temp. 76 degrees @ 3'-heavy boat traffic Sunday.
Wind dead calm- cloudless sky- 60 degrees- not even one fishing boat-beautiful day.
85 degrees- sunny- calm-some "glob" type algae-water temp. 76 degrees @ 3'. floating around-heavy traffic on weekend-lowest water level of year.
3 fishing boats and 1 water skier on the lake.
Wind northeast- cloudy- temp. 62 degrees.- light boat activity- water temp. @3' = 63 degrees.
Nice day- wind light se- temp. 78 degrees.- water temp. @3' = 70 degrees.
Weather nice- cloudy- light wind- mod. boating activity- air temp. 78 degrees.
Wind N @ 5 mph- overcast- air temp. 68 degrees. no boating activity.
79 degrees. Light wind (variable)- 80 degrees. water temp. @ 3 feet- sunny- moderate boating activity.
Storm 7/1/97- high winds- heavy rain- branches down- etc. debris in water.
Air temp. 74 degrees. water temp. 72 degrees. @ 3 feet- sunny few cumulus- 3 boats- wind light and variable- people at the beach.
92 degrees. very windy- partly cloudy- heavy use of beach area- moderate boat traffic.
78 degrees. Light SE wind- partly cloudy- best secchi in 2 years.
Light variable wind- 79 degrees- sunny- mod. activity on the lake and beach.
Light SW wind- sunny- light activity- 7 loons on lake @7 A.M.
Overcast- 66 degrees. no boats- wind NW @ 5 mph. water temp. 70 degrees.
Light activity- sunny 80 degrees- wind NW at 15 mph.
NW wind 10 mph. 73 degrees F. no boats.
S wind 10-15 mph. partly cloudy and 82 degrees. five fishing boats.
Overcast and choppy. NW wind 10 mph and 60 degrees.
Overcast and light breeze from the east. 68 degrees.
Overcast and light NE wind. 80 degrees.
Partly cloudy and 84 degrees. water temp 80 degrees at 3 feet.
Sunny- 84 degrees. water temp is 80 degrees at 3 feet.
Mostly cloudy with light N wind. no activity . 78 degrees.
Cloudy and light N wind. 80 degrees.
Sunny- WNW wind at 10 mph. 76 degrees.
Sunny- NW wind at 8-10 mph. 80 degrees.
Hazy- almost calm. 80 degrees. water temp is 80 degrees at 3 feet.
Sunny and 80 degrees. SW breeze.  Water temp is 80 degrees.
Sunny- light breeze from the south. two boats.
Sunny and calm. 72 degrees- no activity.
Partly cloudy. wind S @ 8-10. 2 boats on lake. saw 4 immature loons in morning.
Sunny. light SW wind. 2 boats on lake. put the no wake buoys in this am. air temp 73 F.
Sunny. wind N @ 5 mph. 3 boats. air temp 60 F. water temp 68 F.
Overcast. light SE wind. no boats. air temp 78 F.high winds 06/05. water temp 76 F.
Mostly sunny. wind NW @ 5-10. no activity on lake. air temp 65 F. pleasant day. water temp 72 F.
Sunny. wind W @ 5 mph. no boats. about 12 persons at beach. air temp 80 F. water temp 76 F.
Mostly sunny. WNW wind @ 5 mph. no boats. air 70 F. pleasant day. a little cool for swimming. 6 loons @ 7: 00 am. water temp 76 F.
Overcast. wind SE @ 5-10. 2 boats. air temp 65 F. .25" rain this am. water temp 80 F.
Sunny. wind SW @ 5. 2 boats. people at beach. air temp 88 F. fine day. water temp 82 F.
Sunny. wind variable. 2 boats. 2 loons. people @ beach. air temp 86 F. pleasant day. water temp 80 F.
Sunny- very humid. 84 F. wind NW @ 5. 12 people @ beach. no fishermen. water temp 82 F.
Overcast. 78 F. wind SW @ 8-10. water skiers. people on beach. 3 loons. no fishermen. water temp 80 F.
Wind sse @ 5. temp 82 F. moderate beach use. 2 boats. water temp 80 F.
Partly cloudy. very light SW breeze. temp 74 F. light activity on water and @ beach. water temp 76 F.
Mostly sunny. light variable breeze. temp 82 F. light activity on water + beach. water temp 78 F.
Cloudless. light SE breeze. temp 78 F. no activity on lake. beautiful day. water temp 76 F.
Cloudy- SW wind @ 15 mph- temp 58 F- no boating activity. water temp 70 F.
Mostly sunny- light NW wind- temp 65 F- 2 fishing boats- buoys are removed. water temp 65 F.
Overcast- light northeast wind- no boats- no activity on beach- the air temperature is 66 degrees and the lake temperature is 64 degrees at three feet of water.
Overcast- wind variable- one boat- no activity at beach- the air temperature is 71 degrees and the water temperature is 66 degrees in three feet of water.
Cloudy- northwest wind at 10 mph- three boats- no beach activity- 2" of rain in the last two days- the air temperature is 62 degrees and the water is 66 degrees at three feet of water.
Overcast- light south wind- no boats- no activity at beach- the air temperature is 65 degrees- and the water temperature is 68 degrees at three and five feet of water.
Overcast- light southwest wind- no boats- no beach activity- the air temperature is 63 degrees and the water temperature is 70 degrees at three feet.
Overcast- very light breeze- two boats- no beach activity- the air temperature is 79 degrees and the water temperature is 76 degrees at three feet.
Mostly sunny- southwest wind at 9 mph- two boats- moderate beach activity- the air temperature is 82 degrees and the water temperature is 79 degrees at three feet.
Light overcast- light southeast breeze- three boats- moderate beach activity (it was heavy over the weekend) - the air temperature is 78 degrees and the water temperature is 79 degrees.
Partly cloudy- light southeast wind- no boats- a few at beach- air temperature is 78 degrees and water temperature is 79 degrees.  There were high winds on the 8th and 3+" of rain.
Sunny- light northwest wind- one boat- some at beach- the air temperature is 70 degrees and the water temperature is 79 degrees at three feet.
Partly cloudy- northwest wind at 8 mph- light activity on lake and beach- the air temperature is 76 degrees and the water temperature is 76 degrees at three feet.
Mostly sunny- light southwest breeze- two boats on lake- no beach activity- air temperature is 72 degrees- and water temperature is 79 degrees at three feet- beautiful day.

Sunny- light northwest wind- two boats- two loons- no beach activity- air temperature is 80 degrees and water temperature is 80 degrees at three feet- perfect day.  There were thunder storms on the 12th.
Sunny- light southeast wind- two boats- no park activity- air is 65 degrees- water is 75 degrees at three feet- and 2" of rain since last secchi reading.
Sunny- light east wind- one boat- no beach activity- the air temperature is 77 degrees and the water is 77 degrees at three feet.
Sunny- northwest wind at 5-10 mph- two pontoons planting muskies- the air is 70 degrees and the water is 74 degrees at three feet- it is a nice day.
Sunny- southwest wind at 5-10 mph- no boats- no activity on beach- the air is 70 degrees and the water is 70 degrees at three feet-nice!
Partly cloudy- southwest wind at 5 mph- one boat- no beach activity- the air is 68 degrees and the water is 70 degrees at three feet.
Sunny- Light- variable breeze. 5 fidhing boats. Air temp = 75 deg F. Water temp = 70 deg F at 3'.
Cloudy- light NW wind. 1 boat. 56 deg F. Water temp = 61 deg F at 3'. 7-9" rain in the last 7 days.
Cloudy- N wind at 10 mph. 3 fishing boats- no beach activity. Air = 63 deg F- Water = 63 deg F at 3'.
Sunny- very light SE breeze. 1 boat (9 fishing boats earlier). Air temp 72 deg F. Water temp =66 deg F at 3'. Saw 5 loons at 7 am.

Mostly sunny- SW wind at 10-12 mph. High winds and heavy rain on Monday- trees down at most places on East shore. Jet skis- water skiiers- etc. activity on beaches. 72 deg F- water temp at 3'=72 deg F.
Mostly sunny- NW wind at 5 mph. More rain and thunderstorms since last reading. 3 boats- 1 jet ski- beach activity. Air temp 68 deg F. Water temp at 3' is 72 deg F.
Sunny- SW wind at 3-5 mph. No other boats or beach activity. Air = 84 deg F- water= 80 deg F at 3'. Water level dropping slowly.
Overcast- S wind at 5 mph. 1 ski boat. Some beach activity. Air =70 deg F. water temp = 75 deg F at 3'. Water level dropped .2' since 6/28.
Sunny- W wind at 5 mph. No boats. No beach activity. Water temp 80 deg F at 3'. Air temp 76 deg F.
Overcast- SW wind at 5 mph. 6 boats. Heavy beach activity. Air temp 86 deg F. Water temp at 3'=86 deg F.
Overcast- light breeze NNW. 7 boats- moderate beach activity. 83 deg F. Water temp at 3' = 76 deg F.
Sunny- very light Northerly breeze. 2 boats- some activity on beach. Air = 79 deg F. water temp at 3' = 80 deg F.
Mostly sunny- moderate NW breeze. 3 boats. Light beach activity. 70 deg F. Water temp at 3' = 80 deg F.
Sunny- light NNW breeze. 1 boat- no beach activity. 72 deg F. Water temp at 3'=73 deg F.
Sunny- NW wind at 5-10 mph. 1 boat. Light beach activity. 76 deg F air. Water temp at 3'=75 deg F.
Mostly sunny. NW wind at 5-10 mph. No other activity on lake. 67 deg F. Water temp at 3'=75 deg F.
Mostly cloudy- 5 mph S wind. 2 fishing boats. 57 deg F. No beach activity.
Sunny- slightly breezy. No boats. Air 64 deg F. Some geese flying.
Clear- sunny. SW wind at 5 mph. One boat. Air temp 47 deg F. 2 loons on lake.
pH probe and DO probe not working
pH probe not working. DO probe replaced and is now working.
